{
  "stem": "10283.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very much, to be honest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] My grandmother lit candles, and maybe we went there for Friday night dinner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't remember it that much.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just mostly remember the holidays.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we didn't have a kosher home, and my grandmother wouldn't eat in our home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother always said I was too serious and too good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Because I was a single child, and I was pretty good in school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we-- she always complained that I was too goody-goody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wanted me to be more lively.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was-- you know, when-- I was only 10 years old when Hitler came to power, and I-- I was very much affected by that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were a very serious generation of young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We couldn't-- we weren't all that silly and all that, you know, like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were serious from the beginning, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I said, I went to this elementary school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after four years in Germany, you make a test and go to a lycee, so a lyceum.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to a Catholic school for girls to start the gymnasium part.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after two or three years of Hitler, they wouldn't let Jewish kids go to regular schools anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went to the Hebrew gymnasium, which was very good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was accredited as a high school, like-- but in Germany it was called gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was very ambitious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I knew Hebrew, but not enough for this school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I went by trolley car a few times a week to a tutor to learn more Hebrew so I could get into the right classes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had already boys and girls together then in this school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the beginning it was fine, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then when Hitler came-- some girls were very nice about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most girls right away started to discriminate, and they didn't want to sit next to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they'd say, Jews-- Jewish children smell, and they wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It started right away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had-- I had very few friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were a few other Jewish children in that school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the discrimination started right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I always figured I'd go to college and become some kind of professional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it became clear very quickly that I will not be able to do that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after I couldn't-- when it became clear that we had to leave Germany eventually, my parents sent me to a school for girls to learn household, and near-- that was called Wolfratshausen.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was near Munich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there we learned how to cook and to clean.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had some academic courses, but mostly it was for household duties.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was very orthodox, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we-- it was kosher, and we couldn't have meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- there was no more kosher meat in Germany by that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had mostly potatoes and noodles and rice, and I came home 20 pounds heavier than I went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I-- I learned that I was very unhappy there because I didn't quite fit in with the other girls.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was there about eight months, from April.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the summer, we have summer vacation in-- in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was home for six weeks, and I went back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in November, the-- the Kristallnacht started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had mostly-- well, I-- I was small, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had mostly Jewish friends, the children of my parents' friends.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember non-Jewish friends in particular.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the elementary school, I wasn't hated, or I didn't have any disputes there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But friends, I had mostly Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like I said, in school we had the discrimination.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to leave-- pretty soon I had to leave the Catholic lyceum, which was not bad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The teachers, and especially the principal, were very nice, and they were not Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to keep the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember that the-- the principal called me into the office and told me, or told my parents, that she's very sorry, but she cannot keep us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was smart enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She said, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are the next.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because Hitler hated the-- the Catholics, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, but right now I cannot do anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I cannot keep the Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm not allowed to keep the Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So that's when I went to the Jewish gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Jewish school was very good, was also close by, and it was very good.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
